### Complete API Flow Test - Fixed and Working Examples

### 1. Register Regular User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "Test User One",
  "role": "USER"
}

### 2. Register Admin User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123",
  "name": "Admin User",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

### 3. Login as Regular User
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user1@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 4. Login as Admin
POST http://localhost:8080/api/members/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 5. Get All Products (No Auth Required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/products

### 6. Add Product to Cart (Fixed URL - was missing /items)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cart-items
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIyIiwiZW1haWwiOiJhZG1pbkBleGFtcGxlLmNvbSIsInJvbGUiOiJBRE1JTiIsIm5hbWUiOiJBZG1pbiBVc2VyIiwiaWF0IjoxNzUzNzYxMzU2LCJleHAiOjE3NTM4NDc3NTZ9.xGxEAkT42Xa29mmW92Uj8tCcTzUSQmt5NaNE_C6MYtc
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 1
}

